    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just left the dealership. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it's spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this beauty to go to a great home!",
