    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. The S54 power plant features a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system and verified rod bearing service, ensuring surgical throttle response and mechanical longevity. Its Getrag six-speed manual gearbox offers precise shift gates, delivering power to a flawless variable M-differential. The chassis is structurally pristine, benefiting from proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM-spec bushings to preserve original turn-in characteristics. With original paint depth and a clean undercarriage, this vehicle offers the tactile feedback and lateral rigidity expected of a showroom-fresh icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
