    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece that has been preserved in showroom-fresh condition. This vehicle is a literal time capsule; the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish to be found. Inside, the cabin is an oasis of perfection, featuring supple leather that remains soft to the touch with no creasing, and carpets that have been protected since day one. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of weather exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
