      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of analog feedback and mechanical refinement. Powered by a 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six, the M97 powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and high-revving urgency, managed by a precise 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory short-throw kit. The chassis features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping kinematics, while the limited-slip differential ensures superior power delivery through the corners. This example is in concours-ready condition, exhibiting no bore scoring, a pristine undercarriage, and impeccable paint depth. A true driver\u2019s specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a documented service history.",
